Cost of Living in Major International Cities

Zhenzhen Ge
December 12th, 2016

Motivation

  • Where do you want to live in the future?

  • Cost of living probably is your major concern

  • Tell by real data

Project Challenges and Countermeasures

  • Data acquisition -> Thorough exploration

  • Untidy data -> Using R wisely plus small manual work

  • Data visualization -> Dynamic and interactive way

Data Source

My data comes from:

  • Cost of living, property prices, crime, health care, pollution, traffic, quality of life, travel https://www.numbeo.com.
  • A personal blog http://www.jparsons.net/housingbubble/
  • National Bureau of Statistics of China http://www.stats.gov.cn/english/
